| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1167 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e3ef21d-ddf4-534f-96a2-89f45c965526"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
